Map Name: HeLLscraper
Version: 1.0

Description: Yes, I agree. The Counter-Terrorists have a huge advantage over the Terrorists. But If the Terrorists use their Flashbangs properly..
^^
They can easily pwn the Terrorists. Now it is advisable to Restrict the AWP sniper rifle. But Youre the admin.. Youre Choice.
Both Teams Spawn perpendicular to each other! Buy your guns ASAP to avoid getting shot from the oppositions Spawn!
Once Your Guns are bought jump into the Teleportation Fence and BEGIN TO FIGHT!
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!
www.hellclan.co.uk
